Class UserProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • gosuninjas.koinbox.User.UserProfile

  • public class UserProfile
extends Activity
    This class returns the profile of the user. The class holds important public static variables that will later be utilized in other classes. Variables include mynname, myuniversity,myage,myhome,myaway, myuserid, interestpoint, type, desciption. Other classes that use these variables: edit profile, edit interests

                       throws ClientProtocolException,
